{% comment %}
  FAQ Page
{% endcomment %}

<div class="pt-32 pb-24 min-h-screen bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <h1 class="font-serif-display text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-4 text-gray-900">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 mb-12">Can't find what you're looking for? <a href="/pages/contact" class="text-pink-500 hover:underline">Contact us</a></p>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      
      <details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:border-pink-300 transition-colors">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-gray-900 group-open:text-pink-500 transition-colors">
          <span>What is La Hime?</span>
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">La Hime is a contemporary fashion brand that blends Y2K aesthetic with Tokyo-Shanghai streetwear culture. We create playful, trend-forward pieces for the modern fashion enthusiast.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:border-pink-300 transition-colors">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-gray-900 group-open:text-pink-500 transition-colors">
          <span>How do I know my size?</span>
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">Check out our <a href="/pages/size-guide" class="text-pink-500 hover:underline">Size Guide</a> for detailed measurements. We offer XS through L in most styles. If you're between sizes, we recommend sizing up for comfort.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:border-pink-300 transition-colors">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-gray-900 group-open:text-pink-500 transition-colors">
          <span>Do you offer international shipping?</span>
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">Yes! We ship to most countries worldwide. Shipping costs and delivery times vary by location. All international orders are subject to customs duties and taxes.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:border-pink-300 transition-colors">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-gray-900 group-open:text-pink-500 transition-colors">
          <span>Can I cancel or modify my order?</span>
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">Orders can be canceled or modified within 1 hour of placement. After that, items enter our fulfillment process. Contact us immediately at <a href="mailto:contact@lahime.com" class="text-pink-500 hover:underline">contact@lahime.com</a> if you need help.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:border-pink-300 transition-colors">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-gray-900 group-open:text-pink-500 transition-colors">
          <span>What's your care instructions?</span>
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">Care instructions vary by material. Always check the care label in your garment. Most items are hand-washable or machine-washable on delicate cycle. Never bleach or dry-clean unless specified. <a href="/pages/care" class="text-pink-500 hover:underline font-bold">Read our full Care Guide</a>.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:border-pink-300 transition-colors">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-gray-900 group-open:text-pink-500 transition-colors">
          <span>Do you offer gift cards?</span>
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">Yes! Digital and physical gift cards are available. Purchase directly from our shop or contact us for custom amounts and designs.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:border-pink-300 transition-colors">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-gray-900 group-open:text-pink-500 transition-colors">
          <span>Is my payment secure?</span>
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">Absolutely! We use Shopify's secure payment processing with industry-standard encryption (SSL). Your payment information is never stored on our servers.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:border-pink-300 transition-colors">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-gray-900 group-open:text-pink-500 transition-colors">
          <span>Can I use multiple discount codes?</span>
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">Most promotions cannot be combined. However, our student discount (15% off) can be combined with other offers. Check the terms of each promotion for details.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:border-pink-300 transition-colors">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-gray-900 group-open:text-pink-500 transition-colors">
          <span>How do I get my receipt?</span>
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">Your receipt is emailed immediately after checkout. You can also find it in your account under Order History. Digital receipts are valid for all return purposes.</p>
      </details>

    </div>

    <div class="bg-pink-50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-pink-200 mt-16 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-serif-display text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Still have questions?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Our customer service team is here to help!</p>
      <a 
        href="/pages/contact" 
        class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-black text-white rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-pink-500 transition-colors"
      >
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .font-serif-display { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; }
</style>
